```

接下来，我们在 `handleClick` 方法中对 `stepNumber` 进行更新，添加 `stepNumber: history.length` 保证每走一步 `stepNumber` 会跟着改变：

```javascript{2,13}
  handleClick(i) {
    const history = this.state.history.slice(0, this.state.stepNumber + 1);
    const current = history[history.length - 1];
